iTvosY5kQIIrIGUTlbqYExM.jpg","original_title":"Fils de","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1340110,"adult":false,"title":"Redux Redux","video":false,"overview":"In an attempt to avenge her daughter’s death, Irene Kelly travels across parallel universes, killing her daughter’s murderer again and again. As she becomes consumed by her quest for revenge, her humanity begins to slip away—until the cycle is disrupted when she rescues Mia, a sharp-witted teenager already marked by the killer.","genre_ids":[878,28,18,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.3127,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/2LlddzprXEnWsM3WN0Cjnq6GUvd.jpg","release_date":"2026-02-20","vote_average":6.261,"backdrop_path":"/nBTUocp7lHmyrTmD8mTBOYem4ok.jpg","original_title":"Redux Redux","original_language":"en"},{"id":1119539,"adult":false,"title":"Imago","video":false,"overview":"I received a land in Pankissi, Georgia, a valley at the foot of the Caucasus, right by the Chechnyan border, where I was born. In exile, I am thinking of building a house in this remote place, inhabited by descendants of my Chechen clan. But how could I possibly live in such a place?","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0563,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/6o3sUiVnWaqPDe7zCxBHwHa9zb5.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/kZ6omJ5fkHFJXxZTj6VllHadNkn.jpg","original_title":"Imago","original_language":"fr"},{"id":63888,"adult":false,"title":"Mayerling","video":false,"overview":"Crown Prince Rudolf of Austria clashes with his father, Emperor Franz Joseph I of Austria, over implementing progressive policies for their country. Rudolf soon feels he is a man born at the wrong time in a country that doesn't realize the need for social reform. The Prince of Wales, later to become Britain's King Edward VII, provides comic relief. Rudolf finds refuge from a loveless marriage with Princess Stéphanie by taking a mistress, Baroness Maria Vetsera. Their untimely demise at Mayerling, the imperial family's hunting lodge, is cloaked in mystery.","genre_ids":[18,10749,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.8027,"vote_count":46,"poster_path":"/7yV66NIGGJO3Th7KCn8I21Atwtf.jpg","release_date":"1968-10-31","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/pDEBGS3LiLrN3WqfCIlaIF702ob.jpg","original_title":"Mayerling","original_language":"en"},{"id":96529,"adult":false,"title":"A Question of Silence","video":false,"overview":"When three women with no previous acquaintance kill a male shopkeeper in the middle of the day, the female psychiatrist assigned to the case sets out to understand why.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.157,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/uGhs4woh7yfRupCYOYFMFj9DUPN.jpg","release_date":"1982-02-18","vote_average":6.115,"backdrop_path":"/nAsHIKPDpvtz6xfgkkLMJC1nSlC.jpg","original_title":"De stilte rond Christine M.","original_language":"nl"},{"id":1189422,"adult":false,"title":"Close Your Eyes","video":false,"overview":"A young man tries to sleep as a mysterious voice wants to be let in.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.047,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/qr9Won4vI9mYoLiPnUXViVKBaJf.jpg","release_date":"2023-10-13","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/j3DFIg5eGL70SQHKOTguZhLXoek.jpg","original_title":"Close Your Eyes","original_language":"en"},{"id":1182861,"adult":false,"title":"Romería","video":false,"overview":"Marina, 18, orphaned at a young age, must travel to Spain’s Atlantic coast to obtain a signature for a scholarship application from the paternal grandparents she has never met. She navigates a sea of new aunts, uncles, and cousins, uncertain whether she will be embraced or met with resistance. Stirring long-buried emotions, reviving tenderness, and uncovering unspoken wounds tied to the past, Marina pieces together the fragmented and often contradictory memories of the parents she barely remembers.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.2026,"vote_count":41,"poster_path":"/svscmm7MZml1JqBMl62REnbxhj