nto he and his daughters' life, but as the Japanese feudal system unravels, Seibei is still bound by the code of honor of the samurai and by his own sense of social precedence. How can he find a way to do what is best for those he loves?","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":1.4095,"vote_count":348,"poster_path":"/bB2M8UF8wc9flfGWkcgkTTf8Mzr.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-02","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/pNpQf1ZwdKLHo25jFSDisMfqXJl.jpg","original_title":"たそがれ清兵衛","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1263856,"adult":false,"title":"So Much To Do- So little Time","video":false,"overview":"The story of four young people, ShinAe Ahn who is transgender, and three others, pan-sexual, gay, and lesbian respectively, who are fed up with the oppressive and authoritarian conservative government and its influence on the country. ShinAe Ahn decides to run for the office of prime minister, with the help of her friends and supporters. She meets a lot of caring people, and also a lot of haters. The current Prime Minister is not at all tolerant of the LGBTQIA+ community and is trying his hardest to stop any party that does not follow the orders of the conservative government from running without any logical reason to do so. That creates a political divide within the country, as politicians will attack anyone who is and/or who acts differently, or who stands up for people/themselves who they personally don't like. This story however is being told after the fact, a few years after the election, when ShinAe won as prime minister.","genre_ids":[35,10402],"popularity":0.2053,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/vsC5S4OqJf1ZVRMp2dMXSjYydep.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-23","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"So Much To Do- So little Time","original_language":"en"},{"id":8388,"adult":false,"title":"¡Three Amigos!","video":false,"overview":"A trio of unemployed silent film actors are mistaken for real heroes by a small Mexican village in search of someone to stop a malevolent bandit.","genre_ids":[35,37,18],"popularity":2.8992,"vote_count":1109,"poster_path":"/keQ4ra50w1nktSPRPauxpLaAM2F.jpg","release_date":"1986-12-12","vote_average":6.327,"backdrop_path":"/yMlk79kLF4GrqqP1OY0KccYB787.jpg","original_title":"¡Three Amigos!","original_language":"en"},{"id":8321,"adult":false,"title":"In Bruges","video":false,"overview":"Ray and Ken, two hit men, are in Bruges, Belgium, waiting for their next mission. While they are there they have time to think and discuss their previous assignment. When the mission is revealed to Ken, it is not what he expected.","genre_ids":[35,18,80],"popularity":3.3434,"vote_count":5636,"poster_path":"/vz3Vd6nfq9YZrVvyYx5RHFaYKV3.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-08","vote_average":7.496,"backdrop_path":"/dtGxDOcFssdUUTYBr6M6INXTI1e.jpg","original_title":"In Bruges","original_language":"en"},{"id":1259102,"adult":false,"title":"Eternity","video":false,"overview":"In an afterlife where souls have one week to decide where to spend eternity, Joan is faced with the impossible choice between the man she spent her life with and her first love, who died young and has waited decades for her to arrive.","genre_ids":[10749,35,18],"popularity":18.2039,"vote_count":483,"poster_path":"/o8pg20G67BGmQvRkXwstNre062J.jpg","release_date":"2025-11-26","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/fuacZLpnohQtLD0AhtCErcPVL98.jpg","original_title":"Eternity","original_language":"en"},{"id":470861,"adult":false,"title":"Liza, Liza, Skies Are Grey","video":false,"overview":"A teenage girl and her boyfriend set off on an eventful road trip up the coast of California hoping to figure out the meaning of love and life.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.4886,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/54XDVjXruiusiTKLIMzNr1q89C.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-17","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/lbYjniPOnwdPXFpw4gOQ0VwzgiW.jpg","original_title":"Liza, Liza, Skies Are Grey","original_language":"en"},{"id":1258625,"adult":false,"title":"Another Affair to Remember!","video":